items.name: Faded Glory - Men's Original Fit Jeans

Alternately, you can head out with friends to a sporting event or the golf course for a relaxing afternoon.

items.name: Signature by Levi Strauss & Co. Men's Regular Fit Jeans
items.shortDescription: <p>Brought you by an iconic American brand, all men look simply fantastic in Levis. These Signature by Levi Strauss & Co. Men's Regular Jeans offer a classic, slightly relaxed fit through the seat and thigh, and a straight fit from knee to ankle. Think streamlined, but not too tight, perfect for a wide range of style preferences. Pair these Signature jeans with a plain white t-shirt for a relaxed weekend running errands or watching football, or dress them up with a nice sweater or blazer for a night on the town or Casual Friday at work. These regular jeans offer dependable, all-day comfort and are available in two different washes: Dark Stonewash, which is a lighter, classic true blue; and Rinse, a dark and stylish pair that is versatile and slightly more dressed-up. However you choose to wear these Signature by Levi Strauss & Co. Men's Regular Jeans, rest assured that you're going to look and feel your best.</p>
